Charlie Corp -- VPN / remote access onboarding
==============================================

Build tag: charlie-fs/2.4 (M2.s2:{{ smb_fileserver_flags.m2_s2 }})

Standard provisioning
---------------------
- All new hires get an AD account in OU=Crownlands.
- Default Kerberos pre-auth is REQUIRED for every account (per the 2024
  hardening baseline).
- VPN profiles are issued from the dmz portal once the AD account is in
  the "VPN Users" group.

